{"tid":1492972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾受到警暴的巴絲，請聯絡傳真社","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:12:10.000Z","uid":132281,"like":91,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"1544f4dfd4f330798225aaa39659b18611d89c91","tid":1492972,"uid":132281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"【人道危機調查】警方近日對被捕人士使用武力情況屢遭質疑，有市民向傳真社求助，指不少被捕人士受到警員過份暴力傷害，甚至不人道對待。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社正針對警方濫暴問題，以至是否出現人道危機作出全面調查，呼籲被拘捕或拘留期間，受到暴力、不合法或不人道對待的人士，向傳真社提供資料，我們需要足夠資訊，去了解不同時間、不同警署或拘留中心、不同警員濫用武力的情況，作出詳細調查。<br />\n<br />\n如有第一手資料請與我們接觸，資料絕對保密。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法：<br />\nTelegram: 9639 7479 / @FWInreport<br />\nWhatsapp: 9639 7479 <br />\nEmail: leak@factwire.org<br />\n<br />\n#調查往績：<br />\n收集612影片 - 重組事件，揭露警方開槍報細數 (調查仍然繼續)<br />\n防火電線測試眾籌 - 收集防火電線進行高溫測試，揭發本港防火系統風險<br />\n收集樓宇維修資料 - 製作全港首個資料庫，揭示圍標問題廣泛，提供數據參考<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4zK2eq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4zK2eq.jpg&h=13b5f0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/396495580557502/posts/1192251084315277?s=1449257815&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F396495580557502%2Fposts%2F1192251084315277%3Fs%3D1449257815%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Mtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=30307f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/396495580557502/posts/1192251084315277?s=1449257815&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n一定要清算黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807d1d1207b4d527e942973c8fe1a3623ddbac04","tid":1492972,"uid":132281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cc5859454f77debc32540ec120d9294a9ca86e28","tid":1492972,"uid":132281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"請大家一定要企出黎，清算黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c